## 1. Overview

This document describes the architecture for implementing scope-based filtering in the DETECT CCIRC dashboard, based on André/Pierre's requirements.

**Requirements Summary:**
- "Filters needed to create different scopes of analysis" — 4 pre-defined scopes (US, Fortis, BCeF, Japan)
- "Be capable to adapt any time as users" — Users can switch scopes instantly

