## 4. Scope Definitions

| Scope | Label | Filter Logic |
|-------|-------|--------------|
| `us` | 🇺🇸 US | `accounting_site_code_post_acc IN (12309, 40043, 11939, ...)` |
| `fortis` | 🇧🇪 Fortis | `accounting_site_code_post_acc IN (10054, 10056, 10064, ...)` |
| `bcef` | 💳 BCeF | `pmas_code_post_acc = 'PMA_03' AND (lb_site_risque NOT IN ('BNPP Factor France') OR IS NULL)` |
| `japan` | 🇯🇵 Japan | `accounting_site_code_post_acc IN (30448, 48019) AND pmas_code_post_acc = 'PMA_05'` |

---

## 5. Supported Operators

| Operator | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `IN` | Value in list | `{"operator": "IN", "values": ["A", "B"]}` |
| `EQUALS` | Exact match | `{"operator": "EQUALS", "value": "PMA_03"}` |
| `NOT_IN` | Not in list | `{"operator": "NOT_IN", "values": ["X"], "allow_null": true}` |

