## 9. Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| **Boolean columns** | A segment can belong to multiple scopes (e.g., both US and BCeF) |
| **Config-driven** | Add new scope by editing JSON, no code change required |
| **Simple operators** | IN, EQUALS, NOT_IN cover all current requirements |
| **Immutable input** | `compute_all_scopes` returns a copy, original df unchanged |

