## 10. Adding a New Scope

1. Edit `config/ccirc_params.json`:

```json
{
  "scopes": {
    "new_scope": {
      "label": "New Scope",
      "filters": {
        "column_name": {
          "operator": "IN",
          "values": ["value1", "value2"]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

2. Run pipeline — new `scope_new_scope` column will be computed automatically.

